name: TractoRush: Cubed Farm Puzzle
description:
TractoRush is a simple and addictive puzzle game in a farm style that will suit both adults and children.

Move tractor left, right, up and down on the farm.

Any field is a different and unique task.

Ready to start an adventure and stretch your brain?
Download TractoRush, go through each field in the minimum number of moves and get all stars.
